PSP Neon HR v2.0.4

PSP Neon is a fully featured linear phase equalizer plug-in (AU, AAX, RTAS, VST) that offers eight bands of equalization, each of which can be assigned one of seven filter types. PSP Neon uses frequency-domain fast convolution based linear phase algorithms for the best balance between CPU efficiency and phase accuracy.

PSP 2Meters v2.1.0

PSP 2Meters bundle consists two audio level measurement plug-ins: PSP VU2 and PSP PPM2. PSP VU2 offers professional VU metering with accurate overload indicators. PSP PPM2 provides professional European and BBC PPM metering with accurate overload indicators.
